{
  "stem": "20405.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The oldest ones of Polands over there was much stronger than we were because we're big people and stronger that they were showing us how to do it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was working with Dario at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Greek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With whom?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, to the Polish people?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With the hand, with hands, and making movements, something, because we couldn't understand them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't understand us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- they-- they think they show they-- we saw the first time when we went in the crematorium was the four ovens with three people in it all the time, three dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from kind of a big elevator from downstairs of the bunker calling was a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of the people, prisoners, pulling the dead bodies on the elevator, one on top of the other-- who knows how many they could pull over there-- that elevator coming up.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was the ovens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some other people or prisoners, like us, the most of the time were Jewish-- was Greeks, and I'll tell you why.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took us to put them in the crematoriums with the Greeks, because they had about-- in this crematorium, there was about 100 people working in each crematorium when before, why they took about 300, 400 people from Greece.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'll tell you why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'll finish first.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What we saw in the beginning, so was a space in front of the ovens, a cemented space, too long for about maybe-- they used to put three-- three dead bodies in each line.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like that was about 10 lines, about 30 people, 30 dead bodies in each line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we didn't know what to say with Dario.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
